Final Rating: 10 / 10

It is exceptionally rare to audit a homelab guide of this density that does not contain fatal security flaws, permissions errors, or circular logic. The author possesses a deep, senior-level understanding of Docker networking namespaces, AMD Linux driver architectures, and Nextcloud's permission models. Aside from adding the 10.0.0.0/8 subnet to account for Unifi/enterprise LAN users, the guide is functionally perfect.

